Gedit Cheatsheet


Strg + m 			=> Comment marked lines
Strg + Shift + m 	=> Uncomment marked lines

Strg + o 			=> Open new file

Strg + Shift + c	=> Enter Multi-line editing
Strg + e			=> Add Cursor in Multi-line editing
Esc					=> Escapes Multi-Line editing

Strg + Space		=> Word completion 

Shift + F7			=> Start Spell check

Strg + Alt + n		=> Split Window

Strg + h 			=> Find and Replace
